business_context:
Case: SaaS Growth
Observation: Organic traffic stagnated despite high content volume.
Solution: Shifted from keyword-based SEO to topic clusters.
Result: 42% increase in organic conversions in 4 months.

Case: Ecommerce Paid Ads
Observation: High CPC but low conversion rate.
Solution: Funnel-based retargeting and landing page optimization.
Result: CPA reduced by 35%.
